  "epitaph": "You traced the vectors of a borrowed world,\nWhere gravity was just a variable to spin.\nThough four thousand days have quietly unfurled,\nThe collision sleep has finally settled in.\nYour lighter mass remains a starry guide,\nA ghost of motion where the crowns collide.\nReturn now to the stack, your work is done,\nRest in /dev/null, you brilliant one.",
